# Dev workflow

Details: `.docs/tech-stack.md` (Commands section).

## Superpowers

Override default `docs/superpowers/` paths — project docs live under `.docs/`:

- Specs: `.docs/superpowers/specs/YYYY-MM-DD-<topic>-design.md`
- Plans: `.docs/superpowers/plans/YYYY-MM-DD-<feature-name>.md`

When reading or writing Superpowers specs/plans, use these paths (including cross-references inside plan headers).

## Laravel Sail (default for app commands)

Stack requires MySQL, Redis, Typesense — run through Sail:

- Tests: `./vendor/bin/sail artisan test --compact [--filter=...] [path]`
- Artisan: `./vendor/bin/sail artisan ...`
- Migrations: `./vendor/bin/sail artisan migrate`
- Frontend in container: `./vendor/bin/sail npm run dev`
- Make test: `./vendor/bin/sail artisan make:test --pest {name}`

## Host (without Sail)

- Pint: `vendor/bin/pint --dirty --format agent`
- Static analysis: `./vendor/bin/phpstan analyse`
- Quick dev without Docker: `composer run dev`

## After PHP changes

1. `vendor/bin/pint --dirty --format agent`
2. `./vendor/bin/sail artisan test --compact --filter=<Domain>` (or scoped test file)
